{"tid":1851041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇：局部封關後未來兩周關鍵　醫護憂口罩防護能力","createTime":"2020-01-30T00:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T01:12:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"49ea32d2280b4470d16d98db6fb7202d658987e5","tid":1851041,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T00:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1505530_1_L_20200129223932.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1505530_1_L_20200129223932.jpg&h=8b473632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇表示，新型冠狀病毒傳播速度較沙士快，認為本港局部封關後，未來14天是控制疫情的關鍵期。<br />\n<br />\n但有前線醫護人員擔心，醫管局目前提供的外科口罩只屬第一級別，防護能力未必足夠。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局則指，局方採購的外科口罩，能防止醫護人員短時間接觸病人時受感染，強調會確保各醫院的口罩存量足夠3個月使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1600/0*79esqH6s15y9GGpe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1600%2F0%2A79esqH6s15y9GGpe.jpg&h=4a36f7ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c120db65e5fe2a1128aa7023f637a25cab545ad","tid":1851041,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T01:12:42.000Z","msg":"講真就算戴左口罩同眼鏡都仲有機會中招....<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848960</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}